Zombies can be found in the Lair of Tarn Razorlor or the Chaos Tunnels.

If players wish to train on them in the Lair of Tarn Razorlor, the banker Odovacar can be found close to the entrance to the dungeon, allowing easy banking at a cost of 100 coins per use. A toad batta item spawn can also be found nearby for additional healing.
